Who`s this? Again an oldfashioned man with stovepipe hat standing in front of a large conscription-draft-style army table shouting something nobody could understand except figuring out that it's english language. Wild discussions even weeks after the party "I've heard him saying 'Breakpoint' "..." and something like 'swedish'...".

Well incidentally I discovered what he is shouting behind his pedestal. Did anybody see the movie µC5"Gangs Of New York"µC4, eh? A really great motion picture directed by Martin Scorsese, playing in front of an authentic background.

So what I will recitate now is right at the beginning of the film as Bill 'The Butcher' Cutting is leading his gang 'American Natives' against Priest Vallons Irish 'Dead Rabbits' on Paradise Square. Better known as the Five Points neighborhood which is, projected to nowadays, the area around the Foley Square Courthouse downtown Manhattan.


So the Butcher was the challenger and he opened the battle traditionally:

µC3"On my challenge and by the ancient laws of combat we have met on this chosen ground to settle for good 'n all who holds sway over Five Points: us Natives born rightwise to this fine land or the foreign hords defilling it"

µC4Now that these rumors are killed let's go on. The beat heads heavily towards a breakdown and a girlie [we know her face from Little Nell and Magia] is twirling around holding some silky stripes in her hands. And after all that heat there must be a breakdown with fresh clean air ... how about the alps ? So they did. A wide mountain mapped polygon landscape approaches and you as the viewer feel like flying on top of the world...gorgeous!

Before this break ends view falls on a nice formation of objects flying even on top of you. Scenery is turning green and a cluster of cubic objects is stiring up while the camera flies around.

And what the ??? The first greetings part ever since I saw in a TBL demo ;D

Last big effect is the run through a tunnel mapped very neat and even with raytraced shadows and all that stuff. For the pleasure of the whole crowd the demo ends by taking another flight over the mountain tops alpha channeling the title of the production and the beat slightly drifts out into calm silence.
